  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">COTUMU Fortified Beans and Maize Production and Marketing. Koperative Twihangire Umurimo</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Sector: Food Production (Beans and Maize) Beneficiaries: Bean and Maize Farmers Summary: The project funds will be used to construct drying sheds and a warehouse to improve post-harvest crop processing and storage, establish a rotating crop purchase fund, purchase a truck and bicycles for transport, purchase maize shellers and IT equipment, hire a qualified accountant and a qualified coordinator/agronomist, and train staff and members in financial management, monitoring and evaluation, procurement, and value chain development.. Sector: Food Production (Beans and Maize) Beneficiaries: Bean and Maize Farmers Summary: The project funds will be used to construct drying sheds and a warehouse to improve post-harvest crop processing and storage, establish a rotating crop purchase fund,</narrative>
